oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: National Audobon Society membership card
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Membership card for the National Audobon Society issued to Miss Margaret Croft. The expiration date is October 1973.

The National Audubon Society, founded in 1905, is a non-profit environmental organization which advocates the conservation of birds, other wildlife, and healthy ecosystems. The society has nearly 500 chapters in the United States and operates a number of nature centers, bird refuges, and natural areas.
